text:
Good work, Hiori!
The photoshoot turned out really well.

Thank you.
I'm relieved that it went smoothly.

Yeah, the outfit suited you perfectly,
and your charm really came through.

That's...
thanks to the advice from the Producer.

I might have just followed instructions
without thinking if you hadn't guided me.

That's probably overstating it,
but if I could be of help, I'm glad.

But really, it's your own strength that got us through it.
You faced it head-on and got results.

Do you really think so?
I hope so.

I've been watching you, Hiori, and I truly believe it.
I want you to have confidence.

Confidence is... difficult for me...
But I'll try to accept the fact that I completed the job.
